In case of Python 3, the same error also occurs. My test result is as below.

System information

  • Python version: 3.5.3
  • Everything is the same except the python version

Source code information

  • Branch: r1.9
  • Commit ID: e34327d (latest at that time)
  • Just clone without modification

How to reproduce

$ git clone https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow.git
$ cd tensorflow
$ git checkout -b cmake_build_test e34327d766016bf4901d847c6ce9eb671db7abb9
$ mkdir build
$ cd build
$ cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release ../tensorflow/contrib/cmake
$ make VERBOSE=1 -j4  tf_python_build_pip_package &> cmake_build_py3_log.txt

Error message
